Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.03,0:00:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優人 一起去海邊吧 海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.46,0:00:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦 泰三
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.35,0:00:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.35,0:00:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 說到海邊可是心情開放的代名詞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.11,0:00:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體和心靈都完全表現出來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.19,0:00:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊密的交流
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.77,0:00:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.23,0:00:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班長
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.79,0:00:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡單的說 就是為了能和剛轉校過來的野井原同學來加深感情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.94,0:00:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去海邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.84,0:00:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果少主要去的話 我就沒差
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.70,0:00:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會去的吧 笨蛋少主
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.50,0:00:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 就這麼決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.00,0:00:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.30,0:00:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪女孩子買東西可是男人的義務
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.30,0:00:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 泳衣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.89,0:00:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.05,0:00:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說少主你希望我裸泳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.04,0:01:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緋鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.44,0:01:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 少主只要選就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.69,0:01:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就拜託您了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.46,0:01:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緋鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.19,0:01:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不知道怎麼選泳衣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.09,0:01:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.99,0:01:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約凜子不就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.73,0:01:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼突然就下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.44,0:01:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘記吧 鬼斬役
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.46,0:01:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.14,0:01:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把所有的一切都忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.57,0:01:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.39,0:01:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則 你就會…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.34,0:01:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
