Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:37.03,title1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(480,220)}『海貓緊急出動』
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.23,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.18,0:03:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後就沒有再聽到那些聲音了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 真可惜 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.67,0:03:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我在的話 一刀就可以把那種妖怪斬殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.09,0:03:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說妳啊 能不能別帶著那種東西到處走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.56,0:03:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是少主的守護劍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.23,0:03:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論何時 都不會讓這把安綱離手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前我才一不留神 少主就被妖怪給襲擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是襲擊 我倒不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.74,0:04:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主 沒有必要聽他們的廢話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.51,0:04:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次出現的時候不用多說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接斬殺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.66,0:04:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到現在還總是覺得難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.21,0:04:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現實當中竟然會有這種怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.75,0:04:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可別忘了 凜子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.55,0:04:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳所說的怪物 眼前就有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主 到底哪件比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.88,0:05:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布料多的還是少的 還是繩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 別說的那麼大聲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.87,0:05:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 都已經一起來了 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主卻不幫我選 要我如何是好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.97,0:05:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個觸感 87嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.88,0:05:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是88嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.49,0:05:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.93,0:05:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正從來沒有好好量過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.72,0:05:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少穿件胸罩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.11,0:05:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有誰會在和服裡面穿綁胸的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.66,0:05:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 這個胸部之大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是隻貓 到底是吃什麼才長那麼大的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.53,0:05:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.76,0:05:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.54,0:06:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 果然是性感類型的比較合適
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.48,0:06:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 這件呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.34,0:06:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就買這件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.85,0:06:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被看穿了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.70,0:06:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.25,0:06:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人山人海真是累人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.08,0:07:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是不太一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.39,0:07:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緋鞠 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.19,0:07:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主 您喜歡和服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.74,0:07:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然自己這樣說有點怪 但是我覺得我還算是不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.46,0:07:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人都有…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風格或者是形象的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 那個 我也
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.08,0:07:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有東西忘記買了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.17,0:07:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也覺得你穿和服的樣子很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.82,0:08:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是偶爾穿穿可愛的洋裝也不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少 我要為她選一套洋服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是清純的白色比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.50,0:08:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.94,0:08:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想這件會很適合緋鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 先去穿上試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.77,0:08:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 突然這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.78,0:08:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 他們兩個跑哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼一定要躲起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.48,0:08:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.71,0:08:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在幹嗎 緋鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主 因為我只穿過和服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.23,0:08:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不知道洋裝是怎麼穿的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您能幫我穿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒法做那麼害羞的事情啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.33,0:08:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不介意 會被少主看到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.13,0:08:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我介意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:08:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不幫我穿的話 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.73,0:09:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就把耳朵和尾巴露出來喵喵叫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.91,0:09:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 緋鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.75,0:09:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 少主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.09,0:09:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請幫我換衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.15,0:09:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.59,0:09:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 妳平時不都穿著制服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.15,0:09:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被發現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.14,0:09:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.91,0:09:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.98,0:09:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定得真快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是容易被看穿啊 少主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.14,0:09:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.41,0:09:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說女人不是喜歡享受不斷挑選的過程嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩惱不符合我的性格 這件就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.45,0:09:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那麼再試一件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.03,0:09:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那個必要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.37,0:10:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是少主為我選的第一件衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天已經不可能找到比這件更好的了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.51,0:10:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.65,0:10:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的是完美的直球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.60,0:10:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緋鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.73,0:10:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就這麼穿回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.40,0:10:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 大海
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.07,0:10:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊 白色沙灘 巨大波浪 巨乳泳裝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.88,0:10:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著這些你知道該做什麼了嗎 優人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.95,0:10:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 海水浴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.15,0:10:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 更加H 更加H H H H 妄想全開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.02,0:10:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種突然就到高潮的思考 我是很難接受啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣也算男人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.67,0:10:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到那些都不會唉唉叫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.19,0:10:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 在眾目睽睽之下 不要用那種眼光看啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.71,0:11:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝不認識 不 認 識
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海真是寬廣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 優人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.94,0:11:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別值得注意的是 野井原同學的胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.97,0:11:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那形狀漂亮高高隆起的胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.14,0:11:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充滿彈性的質地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.31,0:11:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是全校學生的憧憬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.42,0:11:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實很柔軟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.79,0:11:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼 你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.40,0:11:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽錯了 不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到她的泳裝模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.93,0:11:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是同班同學的特權
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.23,0:11:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就算腦子變很奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.68,0:11:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就用同班同學的特權 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.32,0:11:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你沉到海底去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.77,0:11:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.58,0:11:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然來到這種全是水的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是夠膽量啊 的說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就讓你死無葬身之地 的說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.04,0:12:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緋鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.90,0:12:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在這裡就好 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.93,0:12:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管我 你們去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.45,0:12:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀 難道說小貓是討厭水嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.12,0:12:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢蛋 怎麼可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.46,0:12:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論是泡澡和淋浴不也是沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 腳沒法勾到的深度就沒轍了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.81,0:12:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武士的慈悲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到貓的話 就是魚吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:12:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個借妳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:12:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.02,0:13:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 難得來一次好好玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.29,0:13:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.17,0:13:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優人 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.15,0:13:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便說一句 虎鯨不是魚哦 凜子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.57,0:13:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.09,0:13:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.28,0:13:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 我這件泳裝也是新買的 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.00,0:13:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很適合凜子 非常可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.63,0:13:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛 可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.24,0:13:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YES YES YES
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.98,0:13:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 凜子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.29,0:13:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 撞到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.02,0:13:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂 妳趁機想做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.31,0:13:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.89,0:14:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼喜歡極樂世界的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.60,0:14:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就請你自已一個人去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.79,0:14:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個變態
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緋鞠去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是丟臉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.10,0:14:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是水罷了 竟然沒輒到這地步
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.84,0:14:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道已經漂到很遠的地方了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.62,0:14:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 緋鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.97,0:14:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.60,0:14:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別嚇我啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.20,0:14:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 擔心你才特意來找你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.33,0:14:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴 閉嘴 根本不用來管我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.30,0:15:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手 緋鞠 胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 現在要是放手的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.35,0:15:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會淹死的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 我會扶著的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.67,0:15:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緋鞠 拜託了 放手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.86,0:15:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不管怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.61,0:15:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.78,0:15:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緋鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.40,0:15:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河家的末裔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.04,0:15:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是 這之前的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜水久 的說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.57,0:15:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜水久
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.65,0:16:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼斬者的覺醒會破壞人類與妖怪的平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.38,0:16:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放任不管的話 又會藉著為了人類的名義來殺我們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.68,0:16:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,100年前 我的族人就是被鬼斬者十二家中的一家地走家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.32,0:16:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給趕盡殺絕 的說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.05,0:16:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是想平靜的生活下去而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.74,0:16:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼斬役是禍害 的說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.41,0:16:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.11,0:16:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再讓你動少主一根手指了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.83,0:16:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緋鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓 難纏的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.48,0:16:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用冰柱 妳是蛟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.14,0:16:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野井原的緋劍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.79,0:16:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到現在這個時代還在追隨著天河家族嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:16:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.90,0:17:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錦鉿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.63,0:17:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是不擇手段的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點小事 不算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.55,0:17:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真難纏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緋鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.15,0:17:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點程度而已 不用擔心我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.93,0:17:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.22,0:17:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.71,0:17:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緋鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.36,0:17:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:18:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然自投羅網 還真是愚蠢的鬼斬役呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.03,0:18:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經無法再出來 的說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.66,0:18:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,省了我不少麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.88,0:18:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把你們兩個人一起收拾掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.45,0:18:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.06,0:18:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刨冰讓我的力量增加了三倍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.36,0:18:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連魚也會被淹死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.90,0:18:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死 的說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.34,0:18:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓 妳做了什麼 的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.04,0:19:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緋鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.39,0:19:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然做出這種難以想像的事 的說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.92,0:19:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能操縱的只有普通的水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混入其他妖怪的血的話 妳就無法操縱了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.11,0:19:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡還有很多很多的水 的說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.13,0:19:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緋鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.64,0:19:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃吧 少主
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.58,0:19:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會為您爭取逃跑的時間的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.87,0:19:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是少主的守護劍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.56,0:19:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守護您是我的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.68,0:20:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.85,0:20:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.42,0:20:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼可能一個人逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.19,0:20:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了救我受了那麼重的傷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一緋鞠出了什麼事的話 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.26,0:20:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我能逃走 也不會開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.29,0:20:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.07,0:20:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了我而犧牲自己這種事我不允許
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是我所期望的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.31,0:20:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河家的鬼斬者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.61,0:20:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓也好 這傢伙也好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.70,0:20:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點奇怪 的說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.13,0:20:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就看在那個單純的笨蛋鬼斬役的份上 放過你們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.86,0:20:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 下一次 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.96,0:20:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會殺死你們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.53,0:21:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼斬者的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.36,0:21:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明可以殺了他的 是你故意放走的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.76,0:21:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是為什麼 靜水久
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.13,0:21:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些事情想再確認一下 的說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.78,0:21:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼還能那麼從容不迫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.56,0:21:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不快點的話 被毀滅的可是我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.37,0:21:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再派別的刺客如何
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.11,0:21:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼斬役非消滅不可
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.14,0:21:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想消滅的話 野井原的緋劍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.75,0:21:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非殺不可
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.18,0:21:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
